{"tid":639631,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人返大陸揼開正骨有好推介","createTime":"2018-04-23T15:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T11:03:14.000Z","uid":32850,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"2d85820b2521325a9afa7340c49d44fd06466f46","tid":639631,"uid":32850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:32:21.000Z","msg":"新手上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到有人介紹富臨酒店，話120rmb揼3個鐘，過左11點又有得免費過埋夜，又近羅湖口岸，好似幾好<br />\n我完全未返過去，都唔知原來揼骨可以咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貼士你地通常比幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪入房比師傅？<br />\n會唔會自己帶毛巾帶油比佢推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順手問埋如果夜晚11點零先返到去，近口岸有咩好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8283f81a10c680a0fc9bd4d7edcbcc55b375479","tid":639631,"uid":12792,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:33:07.000Z","msg":"富臨正骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad756a5d61bfd4d48fe64e46993ba63500cca31","tid":639631,"uid":95542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:35:00.000Z","msg":"平到咁"},{"pid":"d03d8ac05341f5ddb70df4ddcd962450e09456d0","tid":639631,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"富臨都幾好<br />\n陽光酒店都唔錯 招呼幾好"},{"pid":"aa9ec9f875fcd71bc2b8f91f97cffed9edc7f8d3","tid":639631,"uid":21292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港有冇咩地方平平地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6957b0d84ea464e8ec1ca9a344bf8c28a1e52feb","tid":639631,"uid":42569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1